{"tid":663502,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［余文樂冷門歌］還你門鎖","createTime":"2018-05-13T10:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T03:55:39.000Z","uid":153790,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2680212b9a5a12504661de82c6c2111a21e9c16c","tid":663502,"uid":153790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:52:14.000Z","msg":"最近煩惱緊問ex拎番鎖匙<br />\n突然醒起有首咁既好撚應景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HYGkhhu5STc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHYGkhhu5STc&d=l56OeejL4wiwyf4oeJug0kbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=6446ff84\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HYGkhhu5STc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作詞：林夕<br />\n作曲：伍樂城<br />\n<br />\n做情侶　做朋友　都需要漂亮藉口<br />\n但和你　沉默太久　應該說的怎開口<br />\n誰要　隔著電話講分手　無法　笑著陪你走<br />\n誰願意　和你鬥　難聽的　別開口<br />\n<br />\n* 談情說愛是那麼易　然而共聚無話更易<br />\n　沉迷冷戰玩意　我與你也沒法醫　無謂再倚<br />\n　談情說愛就算輕易　如何話別誰又會知<br />\n　好不過　相擁到　半熟時　<br />\n<strong>還掉你那門匙　也出於好意*</strong>"},{"pid":"c8bc501be84b60c4db56fdfc893574e902f7c880","tid":663502,"uid":26106,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:52:54.000Z","msg":"冷門？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc34a82b78957c2b890c9ff72d3f1425f63ba9a","tid":663502,"uid":43924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:55:44.000Z","msg":"《冷門》點可以冇生還者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550d8c4b6468f6d25d1c8f16a64ad6c750610aac","tid":663502,"uid":45384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:56:49.000Z","msg":"有首請食麵幾好聽"},{"pid":"34fb630643146ab4f69d30b1903fe204389c3ecb","tid":663502,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:57:03.000Z","msg":"mk歌"},{"pid":"340e6fbc6e51bf4b58cddaed572ee3173dc40246","tid":663502,"uid":74629,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:58:18.000Z","msg":"門鎖<img sr